OL,3,CInquest into the Gleision mine
OL,4,Cdisaster will have 'laser-like focus'
OL,6,FAn inquest into the deaths of four men
OL,7,Fkilled in a mining disaster 13-years
OL,8,Fago will be conducted with a "forensic
OL,9,Fand laser-like focus" a coroner has
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FThe tragic incident occurred in
OL,13,FPontardawe, in South Wales, when Garry
OL,14,FJenkins, 39, Philip Hill, 44, David
OL,15,FPowell, 50, and Charles Breslin, 62,
OL,16,Fwere killed after thousands of gallons
OL,17,Fof water flooded the Gleision drift
OL,18,Fmine.
OL,20,FThe inquest aims to answer key
OL,21,Fquestions surrounding the case.
