OL,3,CInquest into the Gleision mine
OL,4,Cdisaster will have 'laser-like focus'
OL,6,FAt the time of the disaster, seven men
OL,7,Fwere working underground, but only
OL,8,Fthree survived.
OL,10,FMalcolm Fyfield, the mine's site
OL,11,Fmanager, and MNS Mining Ltd, the
OL,12,Fcompany that ran the mine, were
OL,13,Facquitted of gross negligence
OL,14,Fmanslaughter by a jury at Swansea
OL,15,FCrown Court in 2014.
OL,17,FFollowing the trial, the families of
OL,18,Fthe victims successfully campaigned
OL,19,Ffor a full inquest into the deaths,
OL,20,Fwhich was opened in December 2022.
