OL,6,FOn Friday, a pre-inquest review
OL,7,Fhearing took place at Swansea
OL,8,FGuildhall, overseen by Edward Ramsay,
OL,9,FAssistant Coroner for Swansea and
OL,10,FNeath Port Talbot.
OL,12,FMr Ramsay told the court that members
OL,13,Fof the victims' families had attended
OL,14,Fthe hearing in person and online.
OL,16,FHe said: "I want to acknowledge them `
OL,17,Ftheir grief, their loss."
