OL,3,CInquest into the Gleision mine
OL,4,Cdisaster will have 'laser-like focus'
OL,6,FAdding: "I want to thank them for
OL,7,Ftheir attendance today. I want to
OL,8,Freassure them. There will be nothing
OL,9,Fslip slop or perfunctory about this
OL,10,Finquest.
OL,12,F"I am already of the view that this
OL,13,Finquest needs a forensic and laser-
OL,14,Flike focus on answering where the
OL,15,Fwater came from and who, if anyone,
OL,16,Fknew or ought to have known it was
OL,17,Fthere."
