OL,3,CInquest into the Gleision mine
OL,4,Cdisaster will have 'laser-like focus'
OL,6,FThe coroner said he had been studying
OL,7,Fdocuments about the case including
OL,8,Fthose relating to the criminal trial,
OL,9,Fand detailed maps of the area.
OL,11,FHe told the court: "No stone will be
OL,12,Fleft unturned. I will go wherever the
OL,13,Fevidence takes me."
OL,15,FA further pre-inquest review hearing
OL,16,Fhas been scheduled for 25 April next
OL,17,Fyear, with further such hearings
OL,18,Fexpected to take place before the full
OL,19,Finquest.
